race.description: Paul Finn Memorial Provincial Mdn Plate
race.comment: INTO BROOKLYN (10) kept safe in betting on debut when she covered ground to finish sixth over 1100m at this track. Gets a much better set-up for this and expected to go close. KORITSI (7) just under five weeks between runs at her second career start when a fading fifth over 1200m at Kembla Grange. Should have come on strongly for this and Fitzgerald's claim is a bonus. Each way player. COYOTE (3) even effort on resumption when condition gave out late to run fifth over 1250m at Newcastle. Tongue-tie goes on and stays in the mix. PROBABILITY THEORY (11) slow into stride and never looked a winning prospect on debut when ninth over 1100m at Scone. Kept fresh and expect to see a more positive ride today.
